OL,3,CHow a bowls club in Rugby is helping
OL,4,CKenya prepare for the Commonwealth
OL,5,CGames
OL,7,FKenya's bowls team for the 2026
OL,8,FCommonwealth Games has turned to a
OL,9,Fclub in Warwickshire for support ahead
OL,10,Fof their participation.
OL,12,FBilton Bowling Club collected the team
OL,13,Ffrom Heathrow Airport earlier today
OL,14,F(July 17) ahead of The Games will be
OL,15,Fhosted in Glasgow between July 23 and
OL,16,FAugust 2.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
