OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784560725
OL,3,CHow a bowls club in Rugby is helping
OL,4,CKenya prepare for the Commonwealth
OL,5,CGames
OL,7,FTeam Kenya specialise in playing on
OL,8,Foutdoor bowling greens such as the one
OL,9,Fin Rugby. However, the team will be
OL,10,Fplaying on indoor carpet for the first
OL,11,Ftime at the Games.
OL,13,FIt's because Glasgow 2026 will be the
OL,14,Ffirst to have both Bowls and Para
OL,15,FBowls contested indoors. The Games
OL,16,Fclaims this will offer a "unique
OL,17,Fintimate experience for bowlers and
OL,18,Fspectators alike."
OL,20,FThe rules do remain the same.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
