OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784560725
OL,3,CHow a bowls club in Rugby is helping
OL,4,CKenya prepare for the Commonwealth
OL,5,CGames
OL,7,FTeam Kenya's Nancy Cheiruiyot, who was
OL,8,FKenya's 2025/26 Singles Champion says
OL,9,Fher team is unfazed by the new
OL,10,Fterrain, insisting: "we'll take it
OL,11,Fhome."
OL,13,FShe said: "We've been working at the
OL,14,Fcamp (in Kenya) for a month so we're
OL,15,Fvery prepared, and we'll take it home.
OL,17,F"We haven't played indoor game before,
OL,18,Fit's quite a challenge. But, out of
OL,19,Fthe practice we only need to adjust
OL,20,Fsome parts and we'll be good to go."
OL,26,@vD@FpmvD@Opn
