OL,3,CHow a bowls club in Rugby is helping
OL,4,CKenya prepare for the Commonwealth
OL,5,CGames
OL,7,FTim Fox from Bilton Bowling Club said:
OL,8,F"(The players) literally arrived at
OL,9,FHeathrow Airport two hours ago and
OL,10,Fstraight up to Rugby so they can get
OL,11,Fas much practice as possible over the
OL,12,Fnext few days."
